column5: My Birthday was last weekend so my gf, being the awesome gf she is got me a birthday cake based on one of the bass I caught over the holiday.  Check it out.  Btw I wanted Tacos for dinner so it turned into a Mexican theme, as you can see.
That's awesome!!!! Happy belated!!!
That's sweet.  Very cool gf to do that for you.  Did you use a fillet knife to cut it up?  Happy belated
I <3 the theme!  Solid cake too!
COOL cake!!!  Happy belated Dylon Leechman
HAH Kewl!!  Looks like a comfy pillow too...  Did ya git drunk and pass out on it afterwards??!!  nice HD
No but that would have been brilliant!
was it a nickel?
Your girl is a "keeper".
ya she is lol
That is an excellent cake. Happy Birthday. Kenny G.
That's a largemouth I take it.  Congrats!
Very nice! The amount of thought and work that went into that cake shows just how much you mean to her. Congratulations!
Sorry, glitch caused a double post!
Looks like an Atlantic to me... notice the spots on its tail! Happy B-day.
ya its a largie
lol well happy belated to ya, decent cake. Betcha ate the cheeks first? lol
Looks more like smallie colours with a largemouth. Congrats Happy Bassday.  Very cool.
I'd say its got to weigh atleast a nickel, what did ya get it on?
Which goes to show we can debate just about anything!   My guess would be a marshmallow.
Happy belated Birthday! Your gf and fish, both are keeper:)
